  "detailed_description": "This game is a big team shooting game that took a year and a half to make.<br>The game supports the first person and the third person.<br>Background: In the future, intelligent robots generate autonomy in the process of self-iteration, and they decide to overthrow the rule of human beings. The player will play the role of a human soldier, defeated by a robot attack.<br><br>The game consists of four levels, each of which supports solo and multiplayer play.<br>The game includes automatic rifles, shotguns, submachine guns, pistols, grenades and other props.<br>In the game, players can collect weapons, ammunition, medical and other props in the level, kill the enemy and complete the target task to win.<br><br>The purchase of this game will include the game body.<br><br><br><strong>High-precision modeling, supporting multi-person online</strong><br><strong>Realistic dynamic weather system</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras/397893dab49d1b7eb4b6c978e86cee35.avif?t=1752719726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras_big/397893dab49d1b7eb4b6c978e86cee35.avif?t=1752719726 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>Real day and night switching</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras/9c3577864999f0b86c32b3cc3d153945.avif?t=1752719726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras_big/9c3577864999f0b86c32b3cc3d153945.avif?t=1752719726 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras/18a0787e34b9ad340a359c2acadde95a.avif?t=1752719726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras_big/18a0787e34b9ad340a359c2acadde95a.avif?t=1752719726 width=800 height=450 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "This game is a big team shooting game that took a year and a half to make.<br>The game supports the first person and the third person.<br>Background: In the future, intelligent robots generate autonomy in the process of self-iteration, and they decide to overthrow the rule of human beings. The player will play the role of a human soldier, defeated by a robot attack.<br><br>The game consists of four levels, each of which supports solo and multiplayer play.<br>The game includes automatic rifles, shotguns, submachine guns, pistols, grenades and other props.<br>In the game, players can collect weapons, ammunition, medical and other props in the level, kill the enemy and complete the target task to win.<br><br>The purchase of this game will include the game body.<br><br><br><strong>High-precision modeling, supporting multi-person online</strong><br><strong>Realistic dynamic weather system</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras/397893dab49d1b7eb4b6c978e86cee35.avif?t=1752719726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras_big/397893dab49d1b7eb4b6c978e86cee35.avif?t=1752719726 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>Real day and night switching</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras/9c3577864999f0b86c32b3cc3d153945.avif?t=1752719726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras_big/9c3577864999f0b86c32b3cc3d153945.avif?t=1752719726 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2591580/extras/18a0787e34b9ad340a359c2acadde95a.avif?t=1752719726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/259